<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV61">
<l>vācakañ ceyvatu nampara mētollai vāṉavarta</l>
<l>nāyaka ṉāyaka rellān toḻumavaṉ ñālamuṟṟum</l>
<l>vēyaka māyiṉuñ cōrā vakaiyiraṇ ṭēyaṭiyāṟ</l>
<l>ṟāyava ṉāykkula māyvantu tōṉṟiṟṟu nammiṟaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Making words is our highest: he who is of old worshipped</l>
<l>by all leaders as their leader in heaven, he who sprang with [his] two feet</l>
<l>without slipping even when the space to cover was the whole world,</l>
<l>he our lord came [and] appeared in a cowherd family.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
